The paper discusses the development of a recommendation system using collaborative metric learning for predicting the purchase probabilities of new theatrical releases. The paper involves the use of deep neural networks and natural language processing techniques to generate meaningful representations of products and customer trajectories. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
